128 Choices Coffee Shop
Nondescript but very busy Kopitiam in the Toa Payoh area frequented mostly by the locals in the area. Worth a try for Hua Fong Kee roast meats

Try These:
- Duck and Char Siew @ Hua Fong Kee

The Damage (no drinks): S$10-20 for two
